or 8 times(from 20-29 I didn’t’ die that much total) so I was a little shocked to have had that much trouble with 30 but I’m past it now. Just wondering where everybody else went and how tough/easy it was for you.<br>
<br>
Qene Corleone 35 Wizard Ayonae Ro<br>
