<br>
29-32 go to Marus Seru and solo (or quad) Hoppers and the stone things.  There is also two spots with two spawns of recuso right inbetween the Neth Lair zone and Mons Litalus zone.  I was kiting them 2 at time til they all went light blue or green.  The Hunters are cleric so solo them or they will screw up your kite.  The DD they cast did very little damage to me, but they can heal themselves like no ones business.  At 32, I did cougars in IceClad, but the area is over camped on my server.  I did 32 and 33 there but it was a pain in the ass.  They were formidable blue so xp was pretty good.<br>
<br>
All those are crappy loot, so now I am in Rathe Mountains fighting HG's when I can find a group. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaeanorendarion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daeanor Endarion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/picon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/16/02 8:23:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=359.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/ppic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 30, Where did you fight?</span><hr size=1> Spires outside Paw...but that was the only choice then. No expansions yet. <p><table width = 30%><tr><td align=center style=filter:glow(color=#cc0000 strength=1)><font size=2 color=#ffff00 face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Daeanor Endarion of the Rathe</font></td></tr><tr><td align=center><font size = -1><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23437>~ <i>profile</i> ~</a></font></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urikluz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rikluz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/30/02 12:33:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=359.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 30, Where did you figh