<br>
My routine goes like this:<br>
<br>
Cast Bonds of Force on one<br>
Run<br>
Root<br>
Nuke<br>
Repeat.<br>
<br>
Always have a gate memmed.  Occasionally, one will resist almost everything and run you out of mana.<br>
